---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import BookCover from '../assets/Unfinished-book-cover-transparent-2.png';
const coverSrc = typeof BookCover === 'string' ? BookCover : BookCover.src;
---

<PageLayout
  title="Stay Unfinished — Book by Haider Ali"
  description="Stay Unfinished is Haider Ali's guide to building products that evolve with people, systems, and time."
  image={typeof BookCover === 'string' ? undefined : BookCover}
>
  <section class="border-b border-gray-200 py-16">
    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] md:items-center">
      <figure class="order-last md:order-first">
        <img src={coverSrc} alt="Stay Unfinished book cover" class="mx-auto w-full max-w-sm rounded-3xl shadow-xl" loading="lazy" />
      </figure>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900">Stay Unfinished</h1>
        <p>
          <em>Stay Unfinished</em> is a field guide for leaders, product teams, and founders building in a world that
          refuses to sit still. It's the mindset and toolkit I've used to help enterprises launch faster, learn from
          reality, and scale what works.
        </p>
        <p>
          The book is intentionally published in motion. Readers see how I iterate positioning, structure, and content
          as feedback comes in—proof that unfinished work can still deliver value and momentum.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-2">
          <a href="https://amzn.in/d/fWqtwbF" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#0A84FF] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#086cd1]">Buy on Amazon</a>
          <a href="/blog/unfinished-sample/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-gray-300 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 transition hover:border-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-50">Read a sample chapter</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-10 py-16">
    <div class="space-y-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Inside the Book</h2>
      <p>
        Part manifesto, part operator's manual. Each chapter pairs stories from the field with blunt checklists you can
        use immediately. You'll see how teams ship in half the time, how leaders communicate change, and how AI fits into
        a human-centered workflow.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <li>Frameworks for shipping before perfection gets in the way.</li>
        <li>Ways to build feedback loops with customers, stakeholders, and data.</li>
        <li>Systems to keep distributed teams aligned on vision and execution.</li>
        <li>Stories of missteps, pivots, and the rituals that kept momentum alive.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Formats</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <li>Kindle + Paperback on Amazon.</li>
          <li>Continuous updates on <a href="https://stayunfinished.com" class="text-[#0A84FF] underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">stayunfinished.com</a>.</li>
          <li>Workshop companion deck for teams.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Who it's for</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <li>Design, product, and engineering leaders navigating scale.</li>
          <li>Transformation teams aligning executive vision with delivery.</li>
          <li>Founders building systems and culture at the same time.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-gray-200 py-16">
    <div class="space-y-6 text-center text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Bring the philosophy to your team</h2>
      <p>
        Use the book as a kickoff for a workshop or ongoing coaching program. I'll tailor a session for your team so we can
        turn the ideas into action.
      </p>
      <a href="/speaking" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#0A84FF] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#086cd1]">Plan a workshop</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

